General.Name: Intema Insaat ve Tesisat Malzemeleri Yatirim ve Pazarlama AS
General.Description: Intema Insaat ve Tesisat Malzemeleri Yatirim ve Pazarlama A.S. markets and sells building products in Turkey. It offers ceramics health utensils, armature, bathtubs, shower trays, concealed cisterns, bathroom furniture, ceramic coating products, buried reservoirs, counters and accessories, construction chemicals, kitchen furniture, worktops and accessories, and kitchen and small appliances under the Vitra Bath, Vitra Tile, Artemis, Villeroy & Boch, and Intema brands. The company provides its products through its retail stores, as well as through wholesale channels. Intema Insaat ve Tesisat Malzemeleri Yatirim ve Pazarlama A.S. was incorporated in 1978 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.
